These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, juice, milk
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, turtle, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola | milk | juice |
| Pet        | cat | frog   | pony | turtle    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, spy, family, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, american, chinese, thai
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the chinese is in an odd position##4
4. the indonesian is the person watching horror movies##1
5. the american is on the right of the chinese##1
6. the indonesian is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | horror  | spy  | sports |
| Nationality   | thai    | indonesian | chinese | american    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, peach, cranberry, onion
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, comedy, adventure, fantasy
1. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
2. the person eating cranberry is in an even position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | onion | cranberry | peach    | mango      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure        | fantasy     | sports | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, writing, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, trance, house, metal
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan of rock and the fan of metal##2
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | puzzles | card-games | writing |
| Music-Genre   | house       | rock   | trance    | metal  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, r&b, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, french, argentine, pakistani
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the french is the fan of trance##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
5. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
6. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | dubstep    | r&b   | trance       |
| Nationality   | indonesian | pakistani | argentine | french |

 #################################

 
