.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire, comedy, documentary
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, van, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | documentary | comedy | satire    |
| Transport     | scooter | van  | helicopter     | trike |

