.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, musician, paramedic, designer
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the musician##3
2. the designer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the designer##3
4. the designer is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the accountant is between the designer and the musician##2
6. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the hamster is between the accountant and the owner of the lizard##2
8. the accountant is on the left or right of the musician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | musician | accountant      | designer | paramedic |
| Pet   | goldfish  | mouse | hamster    | lizard            |

