.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, cherry, apricot, apple
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, frog, ferret
1. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
2. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the goldfish and the person eating apricot##2
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating apricot is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | apple | cherry   | onion | apricot |
| Pet    | ferret     | goldfish | guinea-pig     | frog  |

