.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, iced-tea, milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, funk, folk, indie
1. the person drinking tea is the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of indie is between the fan of ambient and the person drinking iced-tea##2
4. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | iced-tea   | tea | milk |
| Music-Genre   | folk | funk | indie        | ambient    |

