.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, sprite, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, skiing, basketball, golf
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee   | cola   | iced-tea      | sprite      |
| Sport      | skiing | basketball | golf | volleyball |

