.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, watermelon, potato, radish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, country, d&b, indie
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
3. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4
4. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1
5. the person eating potato is between the fan of country and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | radish | watermelon  | potato  | nectarine |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | d&b | metal | country   |

