.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, hiking, puzzles, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, climbing, baseball, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | hiking         | sudoku   | puzzles |
| Sport   | baseball    | climbing | swimming | cycling   |

