.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, drawing, skydiving, card-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing, badminton, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | drawing | traveling | skydiving    | card-games |
| Sport   | skateboarding   | badminton  | soccer | skiing     |

