.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, drawing, puzzles, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, argentine, pakistani, italian
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
3. the argentine is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the argentine##3
5. the argentine is between the italian and the pakistani##2
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games   | puzzles | filmmaking | drawing    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | argentine  | italian     | egyptian |

