.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, coffee, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: garlic, onion, apricot, lemon
1. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4
7. the person eating garlic is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice    | coffee       | tea |
| Food       | onion  | apricot | lemon | garlic  |

