.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, polish, french, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, snowmobile, roller
1. the spanish is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the french##1
5. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | polish | french | spanish  | brazilian |
| Transport     | quad-bike      | snowmobile       | airplane | roller     |

