.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, chef, dancer, doctor
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, airplane, motorbike
1. the chef is in an even position##4
2. the chef is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the security-guard and the person driving the car##2
4. the chef is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the doctor##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | security-guard | dancer   | doctor | chef |
| Transport   | motorbike          | snowmobile | car         | airplane  |

 